result.name: The Langham Hong Kong

reviews.text: Loved this hotel in Hong Kong, stunning decor, friendly staff, seamless check in and check out. We also received complimentary drinks vouchers. We weren't happy with the location of our room and the next day we were moved to a different room. Don't go for a room on the top floor as the elevators don't go all the way. Nevertheless, they happily moved us. Location is fantastic, close to the subway and loads of shopping places and great places to eat at. Hotel concierge also easily called a taxi for us, on our way back to the airport. Since we had a late flight, they also stored our bags for us.

Good service, the concierge was always helpful and had excellent recommendations. The hotel staff were super courteous and all our requests were met. House cleaning does a thorough job. We had a city view suite and the only issue was the shower design. It was a very odd shape that made it inconvenient to shower and their fixtures often got in the way. We did enjoy the delicious room service!

Seriously stunning and amazing! My family and I stayed at the Langham 1 bedroom suite this June and we were left speechless. The rooms were impeccably clean and spacious. The staff at the lounge on the 11th floor were absolutely polite and reached out to us whenever we needed help. This hotel is a must-stay in Hong Kong and 100% a recommended hotel based on its great location, staff, rooms and facilities.

Very conveniently located hotel with exquisite interior styling and great service. The lounge on the 11th floor is very comfortable also with a wide variety of food, snacks and drinks throughout the day. Highly recommended!

Wonderful hotel. Well appointed rooms. Staff couldn't be more helpful. Great facilities including gym and pool. Well located for easy access to MTR and ferries across to Central. Breakfast selection second to none. Highly recommend.

result.name: 香港朗廷酒店

reviews.text:
❌❌🈲❌❌此酒店會把押金與房費刷卡交易碼交換，將原本房費多一倍的金額向刷卡銀行請求付款，我刷卡銀行已經發現這一點，將通報台灣金融市場調查單位，請各位要入住的旅客注意⚠️
我7/12-7-15入住，全部房費加上餐點才台幣3萬多，今天發現被請款了6萬多，刷卡銀行說這種手法很少見，但曾經發生過，請各位注意⚠️

服務很好，很貼心，因為身為當月壽星謝謝酒店為我準備的溫馨禮物，非常感謝，下次來香港還會考慮住這裡。
